Magnetic armor assembly.
The character from the first frame stands still while futuristic armor pieces fly in from all directions as if pulled by magnetic force.
Chest plate locks first, followed by shoulder plates, arm gauntlets, leg armor, and heavy boots snapping into place with metallic clicks and brief sparks as glowing circuitry activates.
A helmet frame closes around the head.
At the final moment, the large futuristic sword flies into the character’s hands and locks into the grip magnetically.
The transformation ends exactly in the final armored pose from the last frame.
